# JSONs en web.php

## Descripción
### 2 Rutas públicas necesarias con respuesta `.json`

<br/>

* 1
#### /.well-known/apple-app-site-association
```
Route::get('/.well-known/apple-app-site-association', function () {
    return response()->json([
        'applinks' => [
            'apps' => [],
            'details' => [
                [
                    'appID' => '5MS87FZM7M.com.grupomaraton.maratonclasico',
                    'paths' => ['/invite/*'],
                ],
            ],
        ],
    ], 200, [
        'Content-Type' => 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
    ]);
});
```

[Abrir](https://maraton-f6ehg9c8g0cdezh6.centralus-01.azurewebsites.net/.well-known/apple-app-site-association)

<br/>

2. 
#### /.well-known/assetlinks.json
```
Route::get('/.well-known/assetlinks.json', function () {
    return response()->json([
        [
            "relation" => ["delegate_permission/common.handle_all_urls"],
            "target" => [
                "namespace" => "android_app",
                "package_name" => "com.juegomaraton.maraton",
                "sha256_cert_fingerprints" => [
                    "7F:3F:49:3E:F7:4C:D0:65:A9:6D:64:83:28:63:73:9F:19:DC:48:8A:4C:A3:64:6A:8C:96:E8:BB:E3:4C:F4:2E",
                ],
            ],
        ],
    ], 200, [
        'Content-Type' => 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
    ]);
});
```
[Abrir](https://maraton-f6ehg9c8g0cdezh6.centralus-01.azurewebsites.net/.well-known/assetlinks.json)

# Modificar ENVTIENDA

### Pasos Cuando llegue ENVTIENDA al Status
* Tomar la orden
* Transferir los items
* Activar los items
* Activar inventario de esos items
* Tomar el fulfillment
* Cambiar de location

**Shopify antes de cambiar location al ENVTIENDA**
![image](https://project-hub-elroi-labs.domcloud.dev/f/c6e5f898-c118-4df3-b380-f2835fc32b86/download)

**POSTMAN**
* Img
![image](https://project-hub-elroi-labs.domcloud.dev/f/40442c3c-fc99-4311-924e-528d73918be8/download)

* Request
`POST`: https://social.samaya.mx/api/shasasb/v4/status-order-change 
```
{
    "Status": "ENVTIENDA",
    "ShopifyID": "#9991741",
    "Paquetera": "SHASA",
    "NoGuia": "CO256753"
}
```

